2002-05-16  Gonzalo Paniagua Javier <gonzalo@ximian.com>

	* TODO: removed task.

	* Makefile: added System.Drawing.dll

	* aspelements.cs: added PropertyTag class.
	(HtmlControlTag): added IsContainer property.
	(ComponentTag): added ChildrenKind property.

	* generator.cs: check whether a control allows or not other elements
	inside it and the type of the elements if allowed.
	(AddPropertyCode): added support for Color properties.
	(NewPropertyFunction): new Function. Output code for inner tag 
	properties inside component tags.
	(ProcessHtmlTag): new function. Manages simple tags and check if they
	are properties of the current control.

